events.name: Web Study Jam
events.description:
â€¢ What we'll do
*A professional accreditation that Google offers
*Aimed at demonstrating an understanding in basic and advanced aspects of mobile website design and development
*You need basic web development skills to take part
*Takes about 3-4 hours + 90 minute exam

The event will be on Saturday, 17 Feb. 2018

â€¢ What to bring
Laptops

â€¢ Important to know
You should be familiar with web basics

events.name: Cloud Study Jam
events.description:
â€¢ What we'll do
Join us for our Cloud Study Jam with our good friends in GDG Nablus! Together we'll work through Google Cloud Platform Essentials labs and other could platforms labs . Don't worry if you haven't had any experience with them. We will start from the beginning.

â€¢ Important to know
Study Jams are a great opportunity to bring members of your community together to learn something in person. These trainings will give your community members a specific skill they can use for personal development or career advancement.
